node.text: #WRC | #RallyEstonia has been a great rally, with lots of experience gained for @msportltd. Teemu Suninen claimed his best result of the season so far in P6, Gus Greensmith also showed strong form after being forced to retire on the Friday. Adrien Fourmaux fought hard for the final WRC2 podium spot but settled for 4th, and 5th place in WRC2 was Tom Kristensson's best result in the class to date!
